              </label>
              <textarea
                name="description"
                required
                rows="5"
                minlength="50"
                maxlength="1000"
                placeholder="Provide comprehensive details:
• Behavior and temperament
• Visible defects or unique features
• Special notes for buyers
• Feeding habits
• Any other relevant information

Quality descriptions build buyer confidence!"
